deviation.name: Fissure Cascade
deviation.description: Fissures rip into the mission, causing the Enemy Level to go up by 1 every 10s. Destroy them to stop the level from increasing further.

riskVariables.name: Bold Venture
riskVariables.description: Enemies deal -15% Damage and take +15% Damage but gain +15% Movement Speed, Attack Speed, and Fire Rate.

riskVariables.name: Alluring Arcocanids
riskVariables.description: As Rogue Arcocanids charge attacks, they pull Warframes towards them.

deviation.name: Unified Purpose
deviation.description: Enemies can target and destroy Conduits.

riskVariables.name: Postmortal Surges
riskVariables.description: Slain enemies burts with Void energy.

deviation.name: Relentless Tide
deviation.description: The Fragmented Tide never stops attacking.

riskVariables.name: Myopic Munitions
riskVariables.description: Enemies will only take damage if a player is within 15m of them.

riskVariables.name: Bolstered Belligerents
riskVariables.description: All enemies have Overguard equal to 50% of their max health.

personalModifiers.name: Secondary Wounds
personalModifiers.description: Gain 1 Puncture Status Effect every time you take damage.

personalModifiers.name: Fractured Armor
personalModifiers.description: Casting an ability reduces armor by 10% for 10s.

personalModifiers.name: Powerless
personalModifiers.description: All Abilities are disabled until the squad kills 50 enemies.

deviation.name: Cache Crash
deviation.description: Consequences of opening a Supply Cache are active from the start and will intensify once it is opened. Failure to open a Supply Cache doubles the kill count required to finish the mission.

riskVariables.name: Jade Spirits
riskVariables.description: Jade Wisps haunt the region. If approached, they chase down the player responsible and transform into Jade Light beams.

riskVariables.name: Heavy Warfare
riskVariables.description: Enemies take 95% less damage from non-heavy weapons. Enemies will drop heavy ammo packs and heavy weapon recall time reduced to 5s.

deviation.name: Pile-On
deviation.description: Techrot enemies attempt to melee attack Hell-Scrubbers, bursting on contact and increasing scrubber contamination by 33%.

riskVariables.name: Miasmite Swarm
riskVariables.description: Techrot Miasmites swarm out of the shadows throught the mission.

riskVariables.name: Myopic Munitions
riskVariables.description: Enemies will only take damage if a player is within 15m of them.

deviation.name: Noise Suppression
deviation.description: Drones fly above Flare, spraying them with Efervon gas.

riskVariables.name: Arcade Automate
riskVariables.description: Enemy guns launch large, slow moving orbs instead of their usual ordnance.

riskVariables.name: It's Alive
riskVariables.description: Within the underground, hostile overgrowths will attack if players stops moving.

personalModifiers.name: Hypersensitive
personalModifiers.description: Duration of negative Status Effects is tripled

personalModifiers.name: Fractured Armor
personalModifiers.description: Casting an ability reduces armor by 10% for 10s.
